rate hike. The Dow Jones
industrial average gained 224

01:54.715 --> 02:03.857 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
points to close near 17750. The
Nasdaq rose 75 points, and the
S&amp;P 500 added 29.

02:03.857 --> 02:10.063 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
