topic of dispute.

02:22.843 --> 02:26.446 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KANIAH CHAPMAN, Student: I'm
really glad they did shut down
the school, because, for all

02:26.446 --> 02:29.916 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
