to undermine peace talks in
Switzerland.

03:36.616 --> 03:41.822 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Supreme Court of India is
laying down the law about air
pollution in New Delhi,

03:41.822 --> 03:46.827 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
