city. The court today ordered a
three-month ban on sales

03:46.827 --> 03:50.964 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of large diesel vehicles,
imposed higher tolls for trucks,
and mandated that taxis switch

03:50.964 --> 03:54.401 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to natural gas.

03:54.401 --> 03:57.037 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Environmentalists welcomed the
moves, and urged India's
government to see that they're

03:57.037 --> 03:59.372 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
put into effect.

03:59.372 --> 04:04.845 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN: They are going to look at
emission standards for vehicles,
pollution from power

04:04.845 --> 04:09.816 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
plants, and public transport
strategy for the industry. It's
a great beginning, and

04:09.816 --> 04:13.487 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
we just hope that this -- the
momentum that we're building up,
this should continue. We

04:13.487 --> 04:15.755 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
must not slow down.

04:15.755 --> 04:21.728 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Air pollution
contributes to more than 600,000
deaths each year across India.

04:21.728 --> 04:26.967 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The highest court in Japan dealt
a setback to advocates of gender
equality. A decision

04:26.967 --> 04:32.706 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
today upheld a law that requires
married couples to use the same
surname. The law dates to

04:32.706 --> 04:38.478 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the 1800s. About 96 percent of
married women in Japan take
their husband's surname.

04:38.478 --> 04:44.718 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
