no-decision in the trial of
officer William Porter, for the
death

05:05.872 --> 05:08.842 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of Freddie Gray.

05:08.842 --> 05:14.447 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
