their quest for justice, and
their personal sacrifice for

06:12.739 --> 06:16.843 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
their time and effort. We are
not at all upset with them.
Neither should the public be
upset.

06:16.843 --> 06:19.512 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They did the best they could.

06:19.512 --> 06:23.416 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: "NewsHour"'s William
Brangham has been in Baltimore
throughout the day today.

06:23.416 --> 06:26.686 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
