ago. He's outside the
courthouse.

06:26.686 --> 06:29.623 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
William, thank you
for joining us.

06:29.623 --> 06:32.425 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I know you have spent the day in
Baltimore. What has been the
immediate reaction to the

06:32.425 --> 06:34.828 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
news of the hung jury?

06:34.828 --> 06:38.999 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Well, when the
word came out outside the
courthouse today, it was like

06:38.999 --> 06:42.068 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
