People started chanting "Black
lives matter, put the racist

06:51.044 --> 06:56.249 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
cops in jail, no justice, no
peace." I mean, there was a lot
of visceral, visceral anger

06:56.249 --> 06:59.853 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and disappointment that there
was no verdict reached today.

06:59.853 --> 07:04.357 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: So, William, is
there any reason that has been
given -- reasons for this
mistrial?

07:04.357 --> 07:09.195 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: No, it's not
clear why the jury couldn't come
to a final decision.

07:09.195 --> 07:14.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it's important to remember,
in this particular case, unlike
a lot of other police killing

07:14.000 --> 07:18.204 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
cases that we have seen in
recent months, there is not
obvious evidence. There is no

07:18.204 --> 07:22.008 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
dash-cam video to show exactly
what happened to Freddie Gray
when he went into the back

07:22.008 --> 07:25.145 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of that van and came out after
multiple stops around the city
of Baltimore in this near

07:25.145 --> 07:27.914 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
fatal state.

07:27.914 --> 07:31.818 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, those other cases were
clearer-cut. You could see a
police officer shooting a young

07:31.818 --> 07:35.755 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
man. In this case, the evidence
is just not as crystal-clear.
But, that said, we still

07:35.755 --> 07:38.925 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
don't know exactly why the jury
couldn't come to a final
decision.

07:38.925 --> 07:44.030 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Now, as we
mentioned, this was the first of
six trials for six officers
involved

07:44.030 --> 07:48.735 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
