day. Is there a sense that this
mistrial will endanger the

07:48.735 --> 07:51.171 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
other prosecutions?

07:51.171 --> 07:54.708 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Well, there is
the possibility that that's the
case.

07:54.708 --> 07:59.012 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
