to be brought to justice.

08:16.629 --> 08:19.699 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And they refer to this simply as
a bump in the road, not anything
calamitous for the

08:19.699 --> 08:21.835 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
