08:21.835 --> 08:25.805 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And did the lawyer
for the Gray family join with
the mayor and the police

08:25.805 --> 08:30.343 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
