because this obviously was a
trigger last time?

08:30.343 --> 08:32.645 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Absolutely.

08:32.645 --> 08:36.383 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
