had happened to that young man.

08:50.096 --> 08:53.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so I think people are very
worried that that might happen
here if these subsequent

08:53.566 --> 08:57.003 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
cases don't come to a verdict
that the community thinks is
legitimate.

08:57.003 --> 09:00.640 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: And a final
question, William. Can officer
Porter be tried again for the

09:00.640 --> 09:03.176 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
