09:03.176 --> 09:07.046 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Yes, my
understanding is that this -- if
he were to be tried again

09:07.046 --> 09:11.951 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
