and try to re-prosecute him.

09:14.854 --> 09:18.258 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But there's no sense of double
jeopardy. If they appeal and
they can bring a second case

09:18.258 --> 09:20.226 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
against him, I believe that will
be able to go forward. But we
will know more about that

09:20.226 --> 09:21.828 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
tomorrow.

09:21.828 --> 09:33.907 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: All right, William
Brangham for us tonight in
Baltimore, thank you.

09:33.907 --> 09:39.913 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now, up it finally went. The
long-awaited and long-predicted
interest rate hike was

09:39.913 --> 09:43.049 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
