09:49.589 --> 09:54.227 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JANET YELLEN, Federal Reserve
Chair: The underlying health of
the U.S. economy, I consider to

09:54.227 --> 10:01.901 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
