10:32.699 --> 10:36.870 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Street Journal, and Tara Siegel
Bernard, personal finance
reporter at The New York Times.

10:36.870 --> 10:39.372 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
