10:48.481 --> 10:48.781 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID WESSEL, The Wall Street
Journal: You sound impatient,
Gwen.

10:48.781 --> 10:50.550 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
