10:50.550 --> 10:54.821 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Well, I think that
the Fed has figured that
interest rates needed to be low

10:54.821 --> 11:00.593 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
