11:43.670 --> 11:46.906 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And she was very careful to
leave herself a lot of
flexibility on that.

11:46.906 --> 11:50.910 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Tara Siegel Bernard,
when we hear her talk about --
