account, but for now it's really
-- it's pretty much the status

12:31.651 --> 12:33.920 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
quo for the most part.

12:33.920 --> 12:39.258 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
