14:02.241 --> 14:07.780 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So this was designed not to
upset anybody. And they
succeeded in that. But if the
economy

14:07.780 --> 14:11.350 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
continues to get better, they
