interest on their savings a year
from now, and people

14:14.721 --> 14:17.457 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
will be paying more for
mortgages a year from now.

14:17.457 --> 14:21.160 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Let's broaden this
out to the global economic
impact. David, are people

14:21.160 --> 14:24.997 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
