what she does in this case as a
cue to what they do?

14:24.997 --> 14:28.134 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DAVID WESSEL: Absolutely.

14:28.134 --> 14:31.170 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
