45:58.356 --> 46:03.494 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes, because the
question is how does Bach and
what does Bach say to Jay-Z

46:03.494 --> 46:08.065 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
