saying to one another?

46:08.065 --> 46:13.237 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WIL BAPTISTE: Honestly, I think,
if Bach were here today, he
would say, good job, fellows,

46:13.237 --> 46:15.873 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
because, honestly, if you think
about -- if you think about
classical and hip-hop, they're

46:15.873 --> 46:19.243 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
