was the producer at that

46:30.888 --> 46:34.992 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
time, the hip-hop producer, so
to speak, at that time. So it's
not so different from today's

46:34.992 --> 46:36.927 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
age right now. You
know what I mean?

46:36.927 --> 46:38.963 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, there's a lot
of similarities.

46:38.963 --> 46:41.365 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: I'm not sure I
have heard that before. Bach is
a hip-hop producer of his

46:41.365 --> 46:43.367 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
time.

46:43.367 --> 46:49.240 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Braxton Saint Hill (ph), age 7,
