told us he'd had a bad cold,

46:53.711 --> 46:56.781 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
but wasn't going to miss this.

46:56.781 --> 47:02.086 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BOY: Hey, Black Violin, when I
