play too with you. All

47:02.086 --> 47:04.789 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
right. Bye, Black Violin.

47:04.789 --> 47:09.960 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Earlier, I had
asked Wil Baptiste and Kev
Marcus where they hope this all
leads.

47:09.960 --> 47:14.098 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WIL BAPTISTE: I think a lot of
kids are now open to listening
to a Mozart piece or a Beethoven

47:14.098 --> 47:16.467 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
piece because of what we do.

47:16.467 --> 47:21.405 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, I think we're creating --
