47:21.405 --> 47:24.842 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
is creativity. Someone that
would never listen to hip-hop is
seeing hip-hop in a different

47:24.842 --> 47:26.877 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
light.

47:26.877 --> 47:32.149 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KEV MARCUS: Whoever you are,
